  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Professional development programme for policy makers on Science Technology and Innovation (STI) management. SDGs: 8,9,10,17</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To train and increase capacity of a cohort of professionals in public Science Technology and Innovation (STI) policy making, capable to design and execute effective policies for improving the country economy and well-being through science and technology. 
PHASE 1 : It has two components. &#xA0;Component I&#xA0;is training workshop &#xA0;executed in March 2017 .&#xA0;Component II&#xA0;was a study visit for 14 policy makers and CTI government managers, to UK that took place in November 2018</narrative>
  </description>
